languages.text: "Ты хочешь звучать гневно, но я чувствую твое любопытство. Понимаю, познание — оно словно дурман. Меня тоже гложет эта жажда нового знания. Но будь терпелив".
"You wish to sound outraged, but I sense your curiosity. I understand. Knowledge is intoxicating. This craving for new knowledge gnaws on me as well. But be patient."

languages.text: 「あなたは激怒しているように見せかけたいのだろうが、私にはあなたの好奇心が見える。私にもわかる。知識とは人を酔わせるものだ。新たな知識へのこの渇望は私のことも苦しめている。だが、耐えるのだ」
languages.original_text: "You wish to sound outraged, but I sense your curiosity. I understand. Knowledge is intoxicating. This craving for new knowledge gnaws on me as well. But be patient."

languages.text: “你想要装出一副愤怒的样子，但我却听到了你的好奇。我能明白，知识确实令人陶醉，就连我都始终渴求着新的知识。不过，你得有点耐心才行。”
languages.original_text: "You wish to sound outraged, but I sense your curiosity. I understand. Knowledge is intoxicating. This craving for new knowledge gnaws on me as well. But be patient."

languages.text: "Ihr möchtet empört klingen, aber ich spüre Eure Neugier. Ich verstehe. Wissen ist berauschend. Der Hunger nach neuem Wissen nagt auch an mir. Aber habt Geduld."
languages.original_text: "You wish to sound outraged, but I sense your curiosity. I understand. Knowledge is intoxicating. This craving for new knowledge gnaws on me as well. But be patient."

languages.text: « Vous cherchez à feindre l'indignation, mais je perçois d'ici votre curiosité. Je comprends. La connaissance est enivrante. Cette soif de nouveaux savoirs me ronge moi aussi de l'intérieur. Patience, toutefois, chaque chose en son temps. »
languages.original_text: "You wish to sound outraged, but I sense your curiosity. I understand. Knowledge is intoxicating. This craving for new knowledge gnaws on me as well. But be patient."

languages.text: «Pretende parecer {mf|ultrajado|ultrajada}, pero noto su curiosidad. Le entiendo. El saber es embriagador. Esa avidez de conocimientos nuevos también me carcome a mí por dentro. Pero debe ser paciente».

languages.text: "Sesinin öfkeli çıkmasını istiyorsun belki ama içindeki merakı hissedebiliyorum. Anlıyorum. Bilgi mest eder. Yeni bilgilerin peşinde koşmak beni de pençesine aldı. Sabırlı ol ama."
